RIP, handsome boy. "There are no bad dogs, only bad people." Loki, a perfectly healthy 3-year old dog was put to sleep by his owners yesterday for allegedly being "aggressive". This incident has sparked outrage online and raises many questions about the other options the owners had and why the Vet agreed to euthanize a perfectly healthy dog.
